title: Guy accidentally texts booty call the wrong message (7 Photos)
text:
View as Slideshow 1 
Twitter user KillerMareCat dodged a bro-y bullet recently after she received a text from a guy she invited over that was clearly meant for his friend. After being invited up for a potential Netflix and chill sesh, this unnamed “gentleman” sabotaged his own hookup by not only forgetting to pay attention to who he was texting, but sending the douchiest possible text he could muster. 2
